{"tid":2438731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深圳化妝品公司員工培訓亢奮狂叫「我比你強」網民：似足神經病","createTime":"2021-03-08T16:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T01:55:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"22294b4a23d24a0c27b3b33e94dd9fe44c342fa8","tid":2438731,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T16:49:06.000Z","msg":"廣東省深圳市百嘉莉化妝品公司的多名女員工，近日被發現在參加培訓時，被要求集體大叫「我比你強」，部份女員工甚至在台上「動手」互相拉扯推撞，現場極為混亂。事件引起網民熱議，形容涉事員工猶如「打了雞血」（指情緒突然亢奮），並留言批評這是內地傳銷公司的典型培訓手法，呼籲「趁早離開為妙」。該公司有員工事後則強調，「這只是一個非常普通的培訓」。<br />\n<br />\n網上片段顯示，該公司的多名女員工當日在培訓會場上集體高呼「我比你強」口號，之後有4名員工被安排在大台上互相叫囂，其中一對女子更出手拉扯推撞。<br />\n<br />\n網民形容涉事員工猶如「打了雞血」，批評該公司的培訓手法像邪教模式，留言稱：「越是不怎麼樣的公司，越喜歡行這種浮誇做作之風！」「這種公司太普遍了，一抓一大把。」「這樣的公司絕對有病，趁早離開，以防神經病上身。」「傳銷模式，無語，有的時候政府要進行監督。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210309/MK2DY6CAJRHWHCG75JBGWEARF4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210309%2FMK2DY6CAJRHWHCG75JBGWEARF4%2F&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=8b6e3c67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210309%2FMK2DY6CAJRHWHCG75JBGWEARF4%2F&h=101680f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210309/MK2DY6CAJRHWHCG75JBGWEARF4/</a>"},{"pid":"4db3baba3f3d1e103cd59cb67fc763ccd0c456e7","tid":2438731,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T16:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e3e66f3a48c5c84e95140916c915ec92d89347","tid":2438731,"uid":258784,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T16:57:24.000Z","msg":"我比你窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11f82956fbaf33901664ec806ba37cee67d7aac","tid":2438731,"uid":181697,"like":28,"dislike":0,"